&lt;li&gt;Experience with B2C sales of SaaS and technology solutions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with prioritization frameworks, roadmapping, and requirements creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
